Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:06.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:22.04,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:28.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:36.63,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:42.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:51.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:58.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:02.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:06.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:12.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:29.72,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:06.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這份真情實感　好想將它傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.30,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了不沉溺於一去不返的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:22.04,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊緊擁抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:28.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷於那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:36.63,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方應該有什麼正等待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:42.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝著那未完結的故事　飛奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷著一顆真誠的心向著那千難萬險之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:51.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}張開心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:58.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循環傳遞著一個訊息　幸福就存於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:02.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下來的少許勇氣　儘管須以眼淚相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:06.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但這或許正是變強的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:12.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}溫暖的迭句　想要永遠將這份珍重守護
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心緒交織　感受著這其中的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以說沒有人是孤身隻影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:29.72,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片藍天下　好想將這份真情實感傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:19.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:28.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:37.80,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:46.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:49.15,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:57.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:06.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:15.83,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:27.03,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:19.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷揣著內心深處收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:28.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}躍入未知的前方　那裡有什麼正等待著我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:37.80,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是與未來共鳴　不斷憶起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:46.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就會生出勇氣　就能變得堅強　也就不再是獨自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:49.15,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（讓你傾聽）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:57.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定會與你相遇　我會帶著真誠的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:06.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接夢想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:15.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與其坐擁這無限的時刻　倒不如追趕那絢爛的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:27.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　總有一天會讓你傾聽那夢中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:49.46,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第6碗  家裡煮的飯、冷了也覺得熱乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思啊  問你借了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一口氣讀完它們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這漫畫的確有很多設定不集中  讀完一轉眼就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊  到一半會分不清敵我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以為40卷前死掉的角色突然出現我也吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  沒錯啊  什麼嘛  你也不是很清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  你最喜歡哪個角色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…夏奈姐最喜歡哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我可不喜歡那麼優柔寡斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著都有點心急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我讀完再促膝長談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥士  冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我很歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重的  我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼點沒事的沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真能下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好遲啊  出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特殊的事卻回來遲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲點回來理由這麼重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在照顧倉鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修一和我負責飼養它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  就因為這個啊  真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些漫畫是從冬木那借來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙還真執著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這部長篇漫畫全收齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結局是成為貴族還是王族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋想看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下冬木就是好孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:03:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我都用敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是尊敬長輩的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬語我還是會用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看對方是誰就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是本質不同啊  明智君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不管對誰都笑著說敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經積得很深了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面也好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒冷可是女人的天敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可不能掉以輕心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒在胡扯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜是久違的大雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯做什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不太現實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp225}　{\fsp1}gratin{\fsp1}{\r}\N兩袋冷凍法式奶汁乾酪烙菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊只有切片麵包和義大利麵而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些食材真夠微妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一手  把剩下的東西全扔進火鍋做大雜燴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸黑會餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃氣罐沒了  儲藏罐也沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要去買菜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經積得很深了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面也好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃現成的應付一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那趕緊準備起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一堆漫畫要讀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯做好了叫我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當自己是千金大小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了  滿足了  開心了  塞滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一厘米都塞不進了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  幾乎把剩下的材料全用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天不去補習一定要去買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便也把這個買了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一包了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順道去下乾洗店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了把外套拿回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰送去的誰去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣明天再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪還在下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯  明天明天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的天氣可出不了門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛剛在電梯口碰到鄰居
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是接下來還要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐槽吐錯地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去乾洗店拿衣服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪有沒有積起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積得好深了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白的雪白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷起來了  回房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟寒冷是女人的天敵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外面去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別磨磨蹭蹭的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪天在院子裡到處跑才是正解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後打算縮在被爐裡嗎  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你在那邊發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來勁了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈選手投出…第一球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你狠  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:11.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進到鼻子裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  站起來千秋  你不會就這點本事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡扯  我會去醫院看你的  絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得這東西有些異樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面我來教你什麼叫「Winter sports」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會點啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開演啊  開演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在胡扯些啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了  好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  差不多就到最佳時機了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在策劃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也燒得太久了點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子的最佳時機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等叻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「久等叻」你個頭啊  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂風情的小鬼給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  這可是下雪天才能享受到的熱水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上…這開放感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍溫了一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太溫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再燒一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這樣泡澡的也只有自家的浴缸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話別這麼刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一會再出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  雪之夜第二幕現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得安心了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面下著雪  卻窩在被爐裡吃點心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  停電了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  馬上就修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴喊喊就能暖和起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為冷才喊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  不會停太長時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那之前還活著的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我有點睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒乾糧  通訊又斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能死在這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋千秋…快說啊  那句台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦  只有一億元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢  那是什麼場景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  貌似有這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很冷了你就不能消停一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室  應該還有點余溫  去暖一會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸黑浴也不壞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變涼了  而且窗戶沒關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰把窗戶打開的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你唄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  是我  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把窗戶關上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題不在這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來  會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把窗戶關上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有點噁心能不能別捏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能這樣取暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼貪心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這個取暖方法就夠好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了  想吃東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有倒是有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎  我要吃我想吃一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凍得硬邦邦可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了那個  都涼到骨子裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕有熱水也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用  因為沒煤氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小麥粉  水和雞蛋攪在一起會有烤薄餅的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做做看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這可不是開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電力還沒恢復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修復還真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時不覺得有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒電原來這麼不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下這麼大的雪居然停電就是鬆散的鐵證
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責人快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫來想怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好教育他一番好讓類似的事別發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點子不錯  好好地做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩晴天娃娃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想死是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  偶爾這樣過一晚也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷就沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  冬木爸爸不在家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一個人沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去看看他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那麼擔心他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定有很多取暖設備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是小孩睡得也太早了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對方是小學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算看上去是那樣…春香  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道發生什麼怪事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  可能已經睡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還醒著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  好了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為鄰居要互相幫助嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木遇到什麼麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲了很久都沒出來  還以為你死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開這種不吉利的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正擔心冬木你一個人該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家為什麼不馬上開門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我剛想睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿這一身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  剛想換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木  把小爐子用的燃氣罐借我們一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:15:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連替換的都有啊  真有心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很冷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了冬木  到我們家玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下小爐子也能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊  不用客氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秉燭夜談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也很閒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  不知道爸爸什麼時候回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大雪天回到家見我不在  肯定會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很想來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個能幹的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一個人應該沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  突然怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼不想來我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那樣  怕爸爸擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是邊說邊在想怎麼拒絕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來就來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不老老實實說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣  我並不是很想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你這德性我就生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣…就別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？想說什麼就大聲說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你等著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…夏奈姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們也加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦  兩位準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不會手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要和他分在一組
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心別人了  趕快還擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣完全不能還擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣組隊完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我來扔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你負責捏雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手凍僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有火就覺得暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真感謝文明的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也多虧了冬木啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得  就住下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真緩和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要不是停電也不會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就這樣取暖就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  好像來電了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬木  在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木在鏟雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯  真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是這麼個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓肉球摸起來真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似根據貓生活的環境  軟度也會有所不同哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野貓常常在堅硬的路面上走  肉球也就硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.51,0:23:45.06,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(370,0)}第7碗  「越嚼越甜哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家貓就軟軟的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.59,0:23:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  下次試著摸摸肉球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
